          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>TRENDYGOLF is excited to announce the arrival of Varley, a contemporary fashion brand that is redefining the boundaries of style and versatility. Founded in 2015 by Lara and Ben Mead, Varley brings a fresh perspective to modern wardrobes with its thoughtfully designed collections that blend elegance with functionality.</p>"
          }
