            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Varley's debut on TrendyGolf marks the introduction of the Club collection—a standout line that embodies the brand's commitment to timeless style and considered design. This collection is the epitome of court-to-club dressing, seamlessly transitioning from athletic wear to chic everyday outfits.</p>"
