        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Club collection features an array of knitted layers, dresses, and skorts, each crafted in classic silhouettes that exude sophistication. Whether you're heading to the golf course, a casual outing, or simply navigating your daily activities, Varley's pieces are designed to keep you looking effortlessly stylish.</p>"
