          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Varley's unique approach to fashion is evident in their ability to create versatile, easy-to-wear looks that effortlessly adapt to various settings. The Club collection offers a range of options that allow you to mix and match, building a wardrobe that works as hard as you do. Each piece is thoughtfully designed to offer both form and function, ensuring that you stay comfortable and chic from one activity to the next. <br/><br/>Explore the collection below.</p>"
